cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on Bayesian optimization, which is a popular machine learning technique used in various fields including robotics and autonomous systems. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.RO (Robotics) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions automatic control and intelligent design, which fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) respectively. Finally, the paper uses Gaussian process regression, which is a common technique in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
